headline: Schwab Declares Common Stock Dividend and Declares Preferred Stock Dividends
summary: WESTLAKE, Texas, October 23, 2025--The Board of Directors of The Charles Schwab Corporation at its meeting today declared a regular quarterly cash dividend of $0.27 per common share.

headline: Charles Schwab’s Q3 Earnings Call: Our Top 5 Analyst Questions
